Interfaces

Interface Workbook

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    Workbook

    public interface Workbook
    The class for the Workbook. A workbook may contain several Sheets. A workbook can be bound to a File in the system.
    Author:
    Jan-Willem Gmelig Meyling, Maarten Flikkema, Jim Hommes
